settings.editor: Hello, I am Rudra Pratap Singh currently pursuing B Tech in Electronics & Communication Engineering from Vellore Institute of Technology. I am IoT enthusiast that's why my majors is in electronics but i also love to work on Android Development and currently i am also working on App that will be out soon on the play store. Just last month (End June 2020) i started learning wordpress so this is just a basic project as asked by mentors.  I have also made many IoT based project which you can check out on Youtube (I am not a Youtuber) and also on my personal blog website Community of Coder.
